  "original_title": "\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0daf\u0dd4\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0dba, \u0d89\u0db1\u0dca\u0db0\u0db1 \u0dc4\u0dcf \u0dc3\u0dde\u0d9b\u0dca\u200d\u0dba \u0d9c\u0dd0\u0db1  \u0da2\u0db1\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2\u0d9c\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0d9c\u0dd0\u0dc3\u0da7\u0dca \u0db1\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dda\u0daf\u0db1\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A gazette announcement from the President about electricity, fuel and health",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "President Gotabhaya Rajapaksa has issued an extraordinary gazette notice stating that electricity, fuel and health services are essential services.",
        "This gazette notice was issued yesterday (03rd) stating that all service work or labor of any description required or to be done in connection with the maintenance and reception, care, feeding and treatment of patients in hospitals, nursing homes, dispensaries and other similar institutions are essential services. have"
      ],
